snippet.title: Mr. Wally Presents: The Pre-Opening Report from Wally World
snippet.description:
Our fearless leader, Mr. Wally (Legal Conglomerate Monopolies CEO) has a special announcement! There's not much else you can do but enjoy it.

Become a Wally Cadet TODAY:
  VOSS Turbo is a retro styled, on rail, twin stick shooter; with controller and keyboard support. Gameplay difficulty will climb as you visit and conquer new worlds. 30 stages to explore, with secrets to uncover, and bosses to whoop. Explore everything the multiverse has to offer!

VOSS Turbo demo is available on steam, try it out before you buy:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1970840/VOSS_Turbo/

Full game to be released by March of 2024!
Help us out by wish listing it on Steam!
